room_title: Escape room "Insurgent's Lab" by CQ Tactical in Tampa
room_description: The Federal Bureau of counter-terrorism needs your help. They’ve tracked down a group of insurgents using a secret lab to create a bioweapon. An attack on a city seems imminent. Your team has been brought in to uncover the formula behind the weapon. Will you be able to stop the insurgents before it’s too late... and still escape the lab? Time is running out and your team is the only hope of preventing a disaster.
